OL,3,CGovernment decision on #9bn Lower
OL,4,CThames Crossing expected today
OL,6,FA Government decision on whether to go
OL,7,Fahead with a new #9 billion road
OL,8,Fcrossing between Kent and Essex is
OL,9,Fexpected to be announced today.
OL,11,FIf approved, the Lower Thames Crossing
OL,12,Fwill be 14.3-miles long.
OL,14,FWork on the project has been ongoing
OL,15,Fsince 2009, and more than #800 million
OL,16,Fof taxpayers' money has been spent on
OL,17,Fplanning.
OL,19,FThe proposal is aimed at reducing
OL,20,Fcongestion on the Dartford Crossing
OL,21,Fwith a new motorway-style road.
