OL,3,CGovernment decision on #9bn Lower
OL,4,CThames Crossing expected today
OL,6,FIt would connect the A2 and M2 in Kent
OL,7,Fto the A13 and M25 in Essex via a 2.6-
OL,8,Fmile long tunnel under the Thames,
OL,9,Fwhich would be the UK's longest road
OL,10,Ftunnel.
OL,12,FNational Highways says the plan will
OL,13,Falmost double road capacity across the
OL,14,FThames east of London, describing it
OL,15,Fas "our most ambitious scheme in 35
OL,16,Fyears".
OL,18,FIt is aiming to start construction in
OL,19,F2026, with the road opening in 2032.
