OL,4,CThames Crossing expected today
OL,6,FThurrock Council in Essex has
OL,7,Fconsistently opposed the project,
OL,8,Fciting negative economic, social and
OL,9,Fenvironmental impacts, but the leader
OL,10,Fof Kent's Dartford Borough Council is
OL,11,Fin favour of the scheme.
OL,13,FLocal campaigners Thames Crossing
OL,14,FAction Group claim the crossing would
OL,15,Fbe "hugely destructive and harmful",
OL,16,Fand a waste of money.
