OL,3,CGovernment decision on #9bn Lower
OL,4,CThames Crossing expected today
OL,6,FThe statutory deadline for a decision
OL,7,Fon whether to grant a development
OL,8,Fconsent order enabling National
OL,9,FHighways to build the road was
OL,10,Finitially scheduled for June 20, but
OL,11,Fwas delayed due to the general
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FIn July, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,15,Fcancelled the #1.7 billion Stonehenge
OL,16,Ftunnel scheme and the A27 Arundel
OL,17,Fbypass project in West Sussex, but did
OL,18,Fnot mention the Lower Thames Crossing.
